identifier.title: Identifier
identifier.description: A unique name for the button to refer to it by in the API. Will give a warning in browser tools if the name is not unique.

vibration.title: Vibration duration (ms)
vibration.description: If the device supports vibration with 'Navigator.vibrate', it will vibrate for the duration set here on touch down.Set to 0 to disable.

baseEntity.title: Base Entity
baseEntity.description: Image Element Entity that shows the base of the joystick.

nubEntity.title: Nub Entity
nubEntity.description: Image Element Entity that shows the nub (top) of the joystick.

order: Move to first touch and fixed
Move to first touch and drags

type.title: Type
type.description: Set type of behavior for the joystick.

hideOnRelease.title: Hide on Release
hideOnRelease.description: Will only show the joystick when the user is using it and will hide it on touch end. This is commonly used if you don't want the joystick to block what's being shown on screen.

identifier.title: Idenitifier
identifier.description: A unique name for the joystick to refer to it by in the API. Will give a warning in browser tools if the name is not unique.

axisDeadZone.title: Axis Dead Zone
axisDeadZone.description: The number of UI units from the position of the Base Entity where input is not registered.

axisRange.title: Axis Range
axisRange.description: The number of UI units from the position of the Base Entity that the Nub Entity can move to and is the maximum range

positionOnRelease.title: Position on Release
positionOnRelease.description: Where to move the joystick on release and can help keep the screen tidy so that there are clear areas to show the game and arrange controls.

vibrationPress.title: Vibration duration (ms)
vibrationPress.description: If the device supports vibration with 'Navigator.vibrate', it will vibrate for the duration set here on touch down.Set to 0 to disable.

numFrames.description: Number of frames to play before looping

isBackAndForth.description: Is animation looped back in reverse

entityDisable.description: Entity that will be disabled after animation ends. No loop only

speed.description: Speed of the water movement (x, y)
Speed of the water movement (x, y)

groundCheckHeight.description: the lenght of raycast to determinate if it is grounded

jumpForce.description: Adjusts the strength of the jump

lerpTime.description: Adjusts the time it takes the character to turn around.

rotationSpeed.description: Adjusts the sensitivity of turning around on strafe mode

touchLookSpeed.description: Adjusts the sensitivity of looking around using touch

povZoomSpeed.description: Speed of camera movement based zoom (3rd person to 1st person)

fovZoomSpeed.description: Speed of FOV based zoom (1st person zoom in, 3rd person zoom out to ultra wide)

maxZoomOut.description: Max distance from camera to head

maxZoomIn.description: Min distance from camera to head

interval.description: How often data should be updated, 0.1 Execute function 10 times per second

upperBodyBlend.description: blending value to upper body mask
